name: CortDAO_Helmet
description: Community to vote on the selection for 2 helmet designs for one team of W Series racing team for 2022 once funded. At the end of the season the helmets will belong to CortDAO_helmet and its future such as an NFT will be decided again by the owners. Wseries is an all womens motor racing series which follows a selection of Formula One races around the world.
payDisclosure: After Juiceboxs fee, 95% will go to Wseries and 5% to cover costs
